567
00:43:56,801 --> 00:43:59,053
Maka itu dia mau meledakkan gedung ini.

568
00:44:00,012 --> 00:44:01,055
Kakakku tak akan berhenti.

569
00:44:01,139 --> 00:44:03,141
Bisa saja dia menembakkan misil.

570
00:44:03,224 --> 00:44:04,517
Astaga.

