00:44:35,631 --> 00:44:37,425
Atur sesuai urutan abjad.

577
00:44:37,508 --> 00:44:38,634
Abjad?

578
00:44:43,139 --> 00:44:44,849
Kedua dari atas.

579
00:44:56,527 --> 00:44:59,155
Pertama, kita harus pasang
pendeteksi kebocoran gas

